  "time_ut": 1656134117,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9c \u0d89\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db6\u0dbd \u0db7\u0dd6 \u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca\u0db4\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dd1\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Impact of a strong earthquake on southern Iran",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A magnitude 5.7 earthquake has shaken southern Iran, according to foreign reports.",
        "The epicenter was reported below the ground, however; no tsunami alert was issued."
      ],
